    <title><![CDATA[Linode搭建Terraria Service]]></title>
    <link href="http://bearwo.com/2015/02/10/Terraria%20Service/"/>
    <id>http://bearwo.com/2015/02/10/Terraria Service/</id>
    <published>2015-02-10T07:53:35.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-02-10T08:28:34.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p> 买了很久Linode的VPS,只部了个Shadowsocket FQ，有点浪费。正好康神也开始玩Terraria了。就自己搭个服务器和小伙伴么一起玩耍了。</p>
<h1 id="步骤">步骤</h1>
<h3 id="首先要有个游戏">首先要有个游戏</h3>
<p><a href="http://store.steampowered.com/app/105600/" target="_blank" rel="external">Steam</a>上可以很方便买到，遇到打折可以十几块到手</p>
<p>Terraria目前只有Win版，所有想要在Debian上运行需要两个工具</p>
<h4 id="mono-complete">mono-complete</h4>
<p>添加 GPG signing key</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">shell</span></div><div class="line">sudo apt-key adv --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.<span class="keyword">com</span> --recv-<span class="built_in">keys</span> <span class="number">3</span>FA7E0328081BFF6A14DA29AA6A19B38D3D831EF</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>添加 package repository</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">shell</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">"deb http://download.mono-project.com/repo/debian wheezy main"</span> | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.<span class="keyword">list</span>.<span class="keyword">d</span>/mono-xamarin.<span class="keyword">list</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>最后</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">shell</span></div><div class="line">apt-<span class="built_in">get</span> <span class="keyword">update</span></div><div class="line">sudo apt-<span class="built_in">get</span> install mono-<span class="built_in">complete</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="TSHOCK">TSHOCK</h4>
<p>建立个目录</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">shell</span></div><div class="line">     <span class="keyword">cd</span> ~/</div><div class="line">     <span class="built_in">mkdir</span> tshock</div><div class="line">     sudo chmod <span class="number">755</span> tshock</div><div class="line">     <span class="keyword">cd</span> tshock</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>下载</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">shell</span></div><div class="line">wget [link <span class="keyword">to</span> <span class="keyword">version</span> you want <span class="keyword">to</span> download]</div><div class="line">     unzip TShock\ [filename].zip</div><div class="line">     rm TShock\ [filename].zip</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在<a href="https://github.com/NyxStudios/TShock/releases" target="_blank" rel="external">这里</a>找到最新的下载地址</p>
<p>最后</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">shell</span></div><div class="line"> <span class="keyword">cd</span> /tshock</div><div class="line"> screen mono TerrariaServer.<span class="keyword">exe</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>按照提示选择下地图和端口之类。</p>
<h2 id="大功告成">大功告成</h2>
